"To access Password Validation settings, you need the "
":ref:`🔑PasswordValidation <PasswordValidation>` permission."
msgstr ""
"パスワード検証設定にアクセスするには、:ref:`🔑PasswordValidation "
"<PasswordValidation>` 権限が必要です。"

