msgid ""
"Your application needs to support the same language as the one selected "
"in this menu. Otherwise the application specific content will be shown in"
" the standard language of the application. E.g. if your application only "
"supports English, but you select Spanish as the Portal language, your "
"application specific dialogs will still be shown in English."
