#: ../../source/portal-user-guide/statistic-chart/index.rst:131
msgid ""
"When users click a chart element, the Portal navigates to the drill-down "
"dashboard containing a widget that shows the detailed list filtered by "
"the selected value. Features that the user can use on the widget are the "
"same as those on a standard widget, including sorting, complex filtering,"
" quick search, etc."
